OL,8,GThey say that the best camera is the
OL,9,Gone you have with you, and while
OL,10,Ganyone can point and shoot a cell
OL,11,Gphone at something and walk away with
OL,12,Ga decent snapshot, to make a good
OL,13,Gimage, a little knowledge of math and
OL,14,Gphysics goes a long way. The problem
OL,15,Gis, words like "math" and "physics"
OL,16,Gcan be just as intimidating to a
OL,17,Gcreative as "art" is to someone with a
OL,18,Gmore analytic approach to the world.
OL,19,GCombine that with a discipline full of
OL,20,Gold white dudes who gatekeep
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
